io.springlets.security.jpa.domain

Class UserLogin

  • java.lang.Object
    • io.springlets.security.jpa.domain.UserLogin

  • @Entity
public class UserLogin
extends Object
    Some applications require the user to have a login in order to gain access to the application. This JPA Entity models the user login given to a user.
    Author:
